      <title>随着富裕人群涌入棕榈岛，迪拜豪宅销量飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/dubai-mansion-sales-soar-as-wealthy-flock-to-palm-shaped-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管该地区地缘政治紧张局势日益加剧，但全球超级富豪继续涌向中东商业和旅游中心，第一季度迪拜标价 1000 万美元或以上的房屋销量增长了 19%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/dubai-mansion-sales-soar-as-wealthy-flock-to-palm-shaped-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:17:37 GMT</pubDate>
